{"tid":119913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"薯片FB: \"這是一封給香港的情書。\"  #今天我們不談一國兩制只談一生一世","createTime":"2017-02-14T06:08:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T12:58:30.000Z","uid":2638,"like":39,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e0543a33d0166e8a8a27f8ee4db6a43a6711aae","tid":119913,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T06:08:31.000Z","msg":"「情人節」的真諦不是情人，而是幸福。<br />\n<br />\n不論你是單身、熱戀、還是金婚，今天應該問的是「你幸福嗎？」近年香港經歷風風雨雨，出現激烈矛盾時，我們害怕禮崩樂壞，當局勢稍為緩和，我們又怕溫水煮蛙。當市民對政府失去信任，疑心重重、草木皆兵，這種撕裂的關係只會帶來痛苦，哪裡還有快樂。<br />\n<br />\n或許我的政綱無法滿足所有人，但我願意聆聽。<br />\n或許我的雙手不能做到所有事，但我願意信任。<br />\n或許我的理念未必完美到無瑕，但我願意坦白。<br />\n<br />\n五年之後的情人節，希望你能夠說︰「我生活在香港，感到幸福。」<br />\n<br />\n這是一封給香港的情書。<br />\n<br />\n#JohnTsang2017<br />\n<strong>#曾太 #適逢今年情人節是2月14日</strong><br />\n<strong>#今天我們不談一國兩制只談一生一世</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高下立見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7184401fc809c1d854bce87b26f9d32b2aea5e4","tid":119913,"uid":44412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T06:09:26.000Z","msg":"#適逢今年情人節是2月14日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22c6ed082a6e3dacca856cc805886f0dba2208f1","tid":119913,"uid":4312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"睇黎開始急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e17ca831c0f0d17717439ada3e1cc1f56329a2","tid":119913,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T06:10:06.000Z","msg":"公關屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.